OL,3,CResidents told to leave as unstable
OL,4,CPlymouth flats 'could collapse'
OL,6,FA cordon has been put in place around
OL,7,Fa block of flats in Plymouth, and
OL,8,Fnearby residents encouraged to leave
OL,9,Ftheir homes, amid fears the building
OL,10,Fcould collapse.
OL,12,FEvolution Cove in Durnford Street,
OL,13,FStonehouse was deemed 'unstable' and
OL,14,Fevacuated last month after a crack was
OL,15,Ffound in a concrete frame in the car
OL,16,Fpark.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
