OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776687066
OL,3,CResidents told to leave as unstable
OL,4,CPlymouth flats 'could collapse'
OL,6,FOn Friday evening Plymouth City
OL,7,FCouncil said a 27-metre exclusion zone
OL,8,Fhad been put in place 'as a necessary
OL,9,Fprecaution to protect the public due
OL,10,Fto a risk that the building ` or part
OL,11,Fof it ` could collapse.'
OL,13,FSome residents in Emma Street Ope were
OL,14,Fbeing 'encouraged to temporarily
OL,15,Fvacate' and stay elsewhere.
OL,17,FRoad closures were put in place around
OL,18,FDurnford Street, Barrack Place, Emma
OL,19,FPlace and Emma Place Ope.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
