FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776687066
OL,3,CResidents told to leave as unstable
OL,4,CPlymouth flats 'could collapse'
OL,6,FThe council said work to repair the
OL,7,Fbuilding is 'taking longer than
OL,8,Fexpected' and 'there is a concern that
OL,9,Fthe state of the building has further
OL,10,Fdeteriorated. '
OL,12,FPlymouth mum who gave birth days after
OL,13,Fbeing forced to leave 'unsafe' flats
OL,14,Fstill in temporary home
OL,16,FA prohibition order was placed on the
OL,17,Fbuilding by Devon and Somerset Fire
OL,18,FService preventing all access to the
OL,19,Fblock, which has been locked and
OL,20,Fsecured.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
