FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776687066
OL,3,CResidents told to leave as unstable
OL,4,CPlymouth flats 'could collapse'
OL,6,FGary Walbridge, strategic director for
OL,7,Fadults, health and communities at
OL,8,FPlymouth City Council, said:
OL,9,F"Decisions about asking residents to
OL,10,Fleave their homes and closing roads
OL,11,Fare not taken lightly.
OL,13,F"The information we have is that there
OL,14,Fis a potential serious risk to the
OL,15,Fpublic if we keep the area open. The
OL,16,Fsafety of residents, pedestrians and
OL,17,Fdrivers must come first.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
