OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776687066
OL,3,CResidents told to leave as unstable
OL,4,CPlymouth flats 'could collapse'
OL,6,F"We will continue to monitor the
OL,7,Fsituation and will work with the
OL,8,Fbuilding's managers and our partners
OL,9,Fto reopen the roads and nearby
OL,10,Fproperties once there is assurance
OL,11,Fthat the building has been made safe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]
